body:
A hotfix release to fix a regression introduced in 2.36.0 Changes: * To use [the native arm64 runner of Github Action](https://github.blog/changelog/2025-01-16-linux-arm64-hosted-runners-now-available-for-free-in-public-repositories-public-preview/), Linux aarch64 binary is now built with Ubuntu 22.04 (Glibc 2.35, Debian 12). Bugfixes: * Chimera Linux logo is now displayed correctly (#1554, Logo) * Regression of 2.36.0 * Fix building on Haiku Logo: * Fix ALT Linux ---
